#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$ 
#SR936 - AJUSTE DE LA DIRECCIėN DE ENTREGA
$ACTION
    Case ACTION
        When "AP_IMPORT"  : Gosub AP_IMPORT
    Endcase
Return


$AP_IMPORT
  If INICIAL Then
    If P >= 2 Then
      P = 0
    Endif
    INICIAL=0
  Else
    If P >= 1 Then
      P = 0
    Endif
  Endif

  If IMPFIC="SDH" Then
     If P=0 Then
        NALBANT=NALB
        NALB=[F:SDH]SDHNUM
     Endif
     P=P+1
     PASADAS=PASADAS+1
  Endif

  If IMPFIC="SDD" Then
    Gosub CORRIGELIN
  Endif

  [F:SDH]SDHTYP=XSDHTYP
  [M]SDHTYP=XSDHTYP
  [M]SDHNUM=NALBANT
  [F:SDH]SDHNUM=NALBANT
Return

$OUVRE
    Gosub OUVRE From IMPSDHS
    Char NALB(20): NALB=""
    Char NALBANT(20) : NALBANT=""
    Integer P : P=0
    Integer PASADAS : PASADAS = 0
    Integer INICIAL : INICIAL=1
    Char XSDHTYP(3) : XSDHTYP="XDA"
    Char DEPURA(50) : DEPURA="INICIO"
Return

$RAZCRE
    Gosub RAZCRE From IMPSDHS
    [M]SDHNUM=NALBANT
    [F:SDH]SDHNUM=NALBANT
Return

$VALID
    Gosub VALID From IMPSDHS
Return

$SAIMSK
    Gosub SAIMSK From IMPSDHS
Return


$CORRIGELIN
  If !clalev([F:SOP])  Then : Local File SORDERP [SOP] : Endif
  If !clalev([F:ITM])  Then : Local File ITMMASTER [ITM] : Endif
  If !clalev([F:XSOH]) Then : Local File SORDER [XSOH] : Endif  #SR936.n

  Read [F:SOP]SOP0=[F:SDD]SOHNUM;[F:SDD]SOPLIN;[F:SDD]SOPLIN
  If !fstat Then
     Read [F:ITM]ITM0=[F:SOP]ITMREF
     If !fstat Then
         If [F:ITM]SAU<>[F:SOP]SAU and [F:ITM]SAU="ENV" Then
             [F:SDD]SAU=[F:ITM]STU
             [F:SDD]QTY=[F:SDD]QTY*[F:ITM]SAUSTUCOE
         Endif
     Endif
  Endif

#SR936 .bn
  Read [F:XSOH]SOH0=[F:SDD]SOHNUM
  If !fstat Then
      [M]BPAADD=[F:XSOH]BPAADD
      [F:SDH]BPAADD=[F:XSOH]BPAADD
  Endif
#SR936 .en
Return

